http-response ^https?:\/\/(kjp|t7z)\.cupid\.iqiyi\.com\/mixer\? script-path = https://raw.githubusercontent.com/sooyaaabo/Loon/main/Script/ChinaFTP/ChinaFTP.js, requires-body = true, tag = 爱奇艺开屏和播放广告

